      <title>摩根大通任命佩特诺和戈里监管合并银行部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/jpmorgan-names-petno-and-gori-to-oversee-combined-banking-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通Co. 提拔 Doug Petno 和 Filippo Gori 领导全球银行业务，这是新商业和投资银行业务联席主管 Jenn Piepszak 和 Troy Rohrbaugh 领导下的首次管理层改组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/jpmorgan-names-petno-and-gori-to-oversee-combined-banking-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 13:23:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗在扭亏为盈之际聘请摩根大通的拉格万担任银行业务主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/citigroup-hires-vis-raghavan-from-jpmorgan-as-head-of-banking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团聘请了摩根大通公司公司的维斯瓦斯·拉加万（Viswas Raghavan）担任银行业务主管兼执行副主席，他从一个主要竞争对手那里挖来首席执行官简·弗雷泽（Jane Fraser），推动该银行数十年来最大的重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/citigroup-hires-vis-raghavan-from-jpmorgan-as-head-of-banking</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 13:03:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
