      <title>MoonSwatch 手提箱在苏富比拍卖行售价超过 60 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/moonswatch-suitcase-fetches-more-than-50-000-at-sotheby-s-omega-watch-auction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[装在特殊行李箱中的一系列限量版 MoonSwatch 手表为慈善事业筹集了超过 50 万瑞士法郎，凸显了收藏家对欧米茄品牌时计的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/moonswatch-suitcase-fetches-more-than-50-000-at-sotheby-s-omega-watch-auction</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 09:22:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西门子能源因风力涡轮机危机而受到投资者的拷问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/siemens-energy-braces-for-first-investor-encounter-since-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首席执行官克里斯蒂安·布鲁赫(Christian Bruch)面临着西门子能源公司股东的愤怒，他们在第一次有机会直接质询首席执行官时寻求答案，因为该公司歌美飒风力涡轮机部门的质量问题已导致创纪录的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/siemens-energy-braces-for-first-investor-encounter-since-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
